FBIS3-41549 "jpten004___94019" JPRS-TEN-94-004 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Environmental Issues 17 February 1994 EAST ASIA AUSTRALIA Government Announces Environmental Aid Project to Indonesia BK0512121693 Melbourne Radio Australia in English 1100 GMT 5 Dec 93 BK0512121693 Melbourne Radio Australia Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The Federal Government has announced the $22 million project to help improve environmental management in Indonesia. Development Cooperation Minister Gordon Bilney says the project will span five years and focus on managing hazardous waste, water and air pollution, and coastal water quality. He said Indonesia's rapid industrial growth, increasing population, and urbanization are resulting in serious environmental problems, particularly in East Java. Australian environmental experts will provide technical advice, technology support, and training.
